    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J815">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Luxury to apprehend</l>
                    <l>The Luxury 'twould be</l>
                    <l>To look at Thee a single time</l>
                    <l>An Epicure of Me</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>In whatsoever Presence makes</l>
                    <l>Till for a further Food</l>
                    <l>I scarcely recollect to starve</l>
                    <l>So first am I supplied --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Luxury to meditate</l>
                    <l>The Luxury it was</l>
                    <l>To banquet on thy Countenance</l>
                    <l>A Sumptuousness bestows</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>On plainer Days, whose Table far</l>
                    <l>As Certainty can see</l>
                    <l>Is laden with a single Crumb</l>
                    <l>The Consciousness of Thee.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
